---
import { DOCS_LEGAL_URL } from "../constants";
---

<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8" data-reveal>
  <div
    class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--glass-border)] bg-card/80 p-6 shadow-card backdrop-blur-md sm:p-8"
  >
    <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-main">
      Responsible use
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-dim">
      Soundsible is a neutral tool for managing and streaming media you have the
      right to use. You are responsible for complying with applicable laws and
      platform terms. See the project’s legal and acceptable-use notes for
      details.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4">
      <a
        href={DOCS_LEGAL_URL}
        class="text-sm font-semibold text-secondary underline decoration-secondary/40 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-secondary"
      >
        Read LEGAL.md on GitHub →
      </a>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
